    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_38.png[/img]{You have %addict% taken to an ad-hoc whipping post. He lays limply against the wood, his fingers splayed out and pinching and clenching. He looks like he's chasing butterflies, and he carries that absent look when %otherbrother% hides him fierce with the whip.\n\n At first, the whipping does nothing, not even as it snaps across the man's back, leaving crescents of crimson. But after a few strikes, he wakes to reality and begins to scream. You come around to face him and ask if he'll swallow his addiction. He nods hurriedly. You let him get whipped again, and ask again, and again he nods. Another whipping, another question, another answer. Finally, %otherbrother% slackens the whip and coils it.%SPEECH_ON%He's dead, sir.%SPEECH_OFF%}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_38.png[/img]{You have %addict% taken to an ad-hoc whipping post. He lays limply against the wood, his fingers splayed out and pinching and clenching. He looks like he's chasing butterflies, and he carries that absent look when %otherbrother% hides him fierce with the whip.\\n\\n At first, the whipping does nothing, not even as it snaps across the man's back, leaving crescents of crimson. But after a few strikes, he wakes to reality and begins to scream. You come around to face him and ask if he'll swallow his addiction. He nods hurriedly. You let him get whipped again, and ask again, and again he nods. Another whipping, another question, another answer. Finally, %otherbrother% slackens the whip and coils it.%SPEECH_ON%He's dead, sir.%SPEECH_OFF%}\""
