  {
    "key": "e13f5c39ab2f084f4c1190fe3cb3f26a9c9129d667093d8161c5e3a25e04b244",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_39.png[/img]{You bow your head to the earth, feeling such shame that you harken to the days when you gave a shite about the old gods. When you look back up, you find your fingers into a grain sack with its contents spilling all over.%SPEECH_ON%Oy captain, we gotta put those to use.%SPEECH_OFF%Looking over, you see %addict% and a white shadow standing behind him. You rush to your feet, but somewhere in all that hustle the shadow departed. You cannot find it nor any footprint and, not wishing to scare %addict% any further, you tell the sellsword to keep a watchful eye on the perimeter. Yourself, you go to your tent for a drink.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_39.png[/img]{You bow your head to the earth, feeling such shame that you harken to the days when you gave a shite about the old gods. When you look back up, you find your fingers into a grain sack with its contents spilling all over.%SPEECH_ON%Oy captain, we gotta put those to use.%SPEECH_OFF%Looking over, you see %addict% and a white shadow standing behind him. You rush to your feet, but somewhere in all that hustle the shadow departed. You cannot find it nor any footprint and, not wishing to scare %addict% any further, you tell the sellsword to keep a watchful eye on the perimeter. Yourself, you go to your tent for a drink.}\""
