    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_39.png[/img]{You pull %addict% out of the barrel and throw him to the ground. He quickly flips around and yells out with perfect clarity.%SPEECH_ON%What the fark, captain?%SPEECH_OFF%It's not %addict% at all, but %otherbrother%. Looking away, you see %addict% stropping a blade. A pale figure shifts in the distance, but when you blink it is gone. You pull %otherbrother% to his feet and tell him to keep an eye out for robbers. He nods dutifully, perhaps sensing something is off with you, or perhaps not wanting to confront you for a mistake. You return to your tent for a drink.}",
